\v 16 \x * \xo 3:16 \xt 1Te 5:23\x*Haiu hanhan M…®t…®k Iuwe h…®rekes, h…®rak haai ke kakr…®ak m…®t nanu werek werek, te hekrit hekrit menmen yaaim o enum mamnen, h…®rak kakrekyi yi eiyu werek werek. M…®t…®k Iuwe kak…®kepi yi niut…®p niut…®p yi eiyu werek.
\p 
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt 1Ko 16:21\x*Hi Pol h…®rekes ewis h…®m hetpi ‚Äúgude‚Äù mau t…®wei heriuwe his mai. Hi heriuwe menmen im heteikni hi hewis t…®wei ik e. Mar keremem hi hewis…®m mau t…®wei yap…®rwe hi hewis m…®t ek.
